results.name: Numbers n such that A120296(n) is prime.
link: Eric Weisstein's World of Mathematics, Harmonic Number
mathematica: Do[ f=Numerator[ Sum[ (-1)^(k+1)*1/k^4, {k,1,n} ] ]; If[ PrimeQ[f], Print[ {n,f} ] ], {n,1,100} ]
